 Hảo","Qin Fen","Gao Maotong","Han Mubo","Yu Naijia","Meng Zidi","Wang Xinting","Wang Chuang","Sha Zi Xuan"],"director":["Wu Jun Xian"],"keywords":[],"time":"29M8S","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"119563","season":1,"vote_average":9,"vote_count":1},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Zhou Yanchen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhou Yanchen","tmdb_id":2082540,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tO6R8vx3jJsaOhCRPE7PvGUWsU9.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2082540"},{"name":"Từ Hảo","name_vi":"Từ Hảo","name_original":"Xu Hao","tmdb_id":2590478,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ga160oB0YlT8sxd80JPTvHBu5go.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2590478"},{"name":"Qin Fen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Qin Fen","tmdb_id":2633280,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mmHRhfapCFDPZn09xfAV6mQsKaP.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2633280"},{"name":"Gao Maotong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Gao Maotong","tmdb_id":3094351,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hbKO08mqWrH1OHoXKehnRxE4MTC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3094351"},{"name":"Han Mubo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Han Mubo","tmdb_id":3094350,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fyLpbFc9BEFy5JhN0ADuAUwuru5.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3094350"},{"name":"Yu Naijia","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yu Naijia","tmdb_id":3125521,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Hmh5ZX4w3EvnxDu6D46JaPTRlA.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3125521"},{"name":"Meng Zidi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Meng Zidi","tmdb_id":2854114,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pTaR9Hpj7qkXBGm0F65JetgPGlD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2854114"},{"name":"Wang Xinting","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wang Xinting","tmdb_id":2377111,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dbs1xDpCwDWEs37vjCf2rmLr9pO.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2377111"},{"name":"Wang Chuang","name_vi":